{"tid":1049842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個註冊護士","createTime":"2019-03-06T14:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T16:37:51.000Z","uid":58141,"like":18,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"280a1755da1983ef2ce6837fba65a571317df515","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"翻工已經翻到心灰意冷，仲要睇住隔離個post咁多人屌醫護，都不禁問自己咁傻豬咁落力做d吃力不討好既野做咩？<br />\n原來我以為既大是大非其實對香港好多人黎講都唔重要，醒覺啦，香港人其實冇大家想像中咁憎共產黨架，最緊要我仆街時都拉埋你落水咁我心滿意足架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生係自己既，已經決定如你地班連登仔所願:「頂唔順咪辭職囉，冇人迫你架」<br />\n諗住向海外發展，睇左英國，加拿大同澳洲既技術移民資料，暫時覺得澳洲門檻比較低，唔知有冇過來人醫護巴打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c9977fe6850c525f184e1bfbfe51a711f284ed","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:46:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98bdee90d0930cf412ef4fccc9237a9313ee1f94","tid":1049842,"uid":235520,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"你接受到新環境既其實可以去試下<br />\n首先你英文要好先 <br />\n澳洲計埋稅雖然無香港咁高<br />\n但workloads比較低 人既質素亦都高好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要知道一樣米養百樣人 <br />\n人多必有白痴 (香港好多白痴)<br />\n上連登高登 勿認真"},{"pid":"e6ab27c03b385dfcc942df980e772b0dee3309a6","tid":1049842,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:50:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ccddcdb01b0dcb511d3ccd50fe9fb9efdef332","tid":1049842,"uid":42879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個身體強壯，徒手打得贏老虎，跟本醫院就冇咩用。<br />\n理得你香港冇晒護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f714d283f0dba559049eaebdf542d285bea555da","tid":1049842,"uid":46170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"打手黎，連登仔都有新移民<br />\n唔洗太上心"},{"pid":"c71192dfbbb7591389dab63555b87c41fef4647a","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98bdee90d0930cf412ef4fccc9237a9313ee1f94","tid":1049842,"uid":235520,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"你接受到新環境既其實可以去試下<br />\n首先你英文要好先 <br />\n澳洲計埋稅雖然無香港咁高<br />\n但workloads比較低 人既質素亦都高好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要知道一樣米養百樣人 <br />\n人多必有白痴 (香港好多白痴)<br />\n上連登高登 勿認真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"澳洲醫護巴打？想問澳洲牌係咪攞左都係好似香港咁比錢續牌就得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35add8038ffae578226a34feb14bde15d9abb920","tid":1049842,"uid":100637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"轉去private試下先啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：轉左幾個月 so far都唔錯"},{"pid":"0b874803673682c52d15c823e164bb3e44de86c1","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35add8038ffae578226a34feb14bde15d9abb920","tid":1049842,"uid":100637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:56:51.000Z","msg":"轉去private試下先啦<br />\n<br />\n利申：轉左幾個月 so far都唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:03:00.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打意見，真正實行移民之前都會入private做住先，不過想走既主因都係因為今次事件令我反省香港(人)冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5c54b2643978db684520cb711de659746d8dd1","tid":1049842,"uid":48178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"澳洲好多昆蟲 尤其啲蜘蛛好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fde88aa218baf70fdecb7eeffa3eefb0eb6e25","tid":1049842,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:05:52.000Z","msg":"打連登勿認真啦<br />\n事實好多人都憎支那人 特別係害到自己利益既時候<br />\n完"},{"pid":"6d45f2abcd9b6b6d968a617dbdcc3d448068bc41","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af5c54b2643978db684520cb711de659746d8dd1","tid":1049842,"uid":48178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"澳洲好多昆蟲 尤其啲蜘蛛好可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:06:14.000Z","msg":"可怕得過d蝗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c88d3a4c42f797fece6826750dc5304a74097a6","tid":1049842,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:21:25.000Z","msg":"連登有邊行未屌過？<br />\n上連登勿認真"},{"pid":"05916854b60148cb8ffe9705bc3f56543dc719fb","tid":1049842,"uid":235520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71192dfbbb7591389dab63555b87c41fef4647a","tid":1049842,"uid":58141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98bdee90d0930cf412ef4fccc9237a9313ee1f94","tid":1049842,"uid":235520,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"你接受到新環境既其實可以去試下<br />\n首先你英文要好先 <br />\n澳洲計埋稅雖然無香港咁高<br />\n但workloads比較低 人既質素亦都高好多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你要知道一樣米養百樣人 <br />\n人多必有白痴 (香港好多白痴)<br />\n上連登高登 勿認真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"澳洲醫護巴打？想問澳洲牌係咪攞左都係好似香港咁比錢續牌就得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:27:30.000Z","msg":"唔係 不過之前都留意過下相關既資料<br />\n<br />\n同埋我有個EX都係護士<br />\n知道佢返工既心酸<br />\n都唔好講佢APN排更咁返工 <br />\n搞到自己身體壞哂 個樣殘哂 <br />\n好明顯咁睇住佢個黑眼圈愈來愈大 D皮膚愈來愈差<br />\n<br />\n同埋特別係香港人對護士好唔尊重<br />\n或者我講白D D病人家屬好多時候都覺得護士乜都唔識<br />\n對住醫生就恭恭敬敬 對住護士就呼呼喝喝<br />\n我知你地其實都懶得同佢地解釋咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2fb110090b01d76e30a6707a48f1e0f4fce40c","tid":1049842,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"你過澳洲多數去返唐人多既醫院，但過外國除稅未別有香港賺咁多，加油<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持輸入海外醫護，支援系醫護唔介意引入大陸人，其實好多醫院亞姐廣東話都講唔正"},{"pid":"742ae0d6ef4df97230f2f1f68efc7d22db71d09a","tid":1049842,"uid":12486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:30:56.000Z","msg":"依排d情緒都好困擾"},{"pid":"b199da688d702ec1596cc7f11ebe00c42dbce4d7","tid":1049842,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:39:21.000Z","msg":"註冊護士又話辛苦<br />\n註冊工程師又話辛苦<br />\n註冊會計師又話辛苦<br />\n註冊教師又話辛苦<br />\n無話你地唔辛苦<br />\n但行行都有自己辛苦之處架啦<br />\n你幾可見其他行業好似你地咁成日出黎呻<br />\n覺得辛苦捱唔住咪辭職搵過份<br />\n行行都係咁架啦，老細唔會無左你唔得<br />\n亦唔好覺得病人無左你唔得，因為你一走就病人頂上<br />\n資本主義社會就係咁運作<br />\n邊個有能力，咪邊個賺到辛苦錢<br />\n我都唔明你地有咩好呻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPS.唔好再屈我話你地唔辛苦"},{"pid":"67de142c4696231527246e80e6c1e0e96c43ddc4","tid":1049842,"uid":200818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e2fb110090b01d76e30a6707a48f1e0f4fce40c","tid":1049842,"uid":73972,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"你過澳洲多數去返唐人多既醫院，但過外國除稅未別有香港賺咁多，加油<br />\n<br />\n利申：支持輸入海外醫護，支援系醫護唔介意引入大陸人，其實好多醫院亞姐廣東話都講唔正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:34:42.000Z","msg":"支持引入啊   等班廢中廢老睇個街症都要俾幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家歐洲做緊護士 同你地香港差好遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d418101519331c51d78ec2e2fb4f60aad7d4e12","tid":1049842,"uid":66050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"考緊英國RN <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}